--  柜员信息表
-- Create table
create table GYXXB
(
  gybh        VARCHAR2(10) not null,
  gyxm        VARCHAR2(20),
  bmrq        VARCHAR2(30),
  gyzt        VARCHAR2(2),
  gyjb        VARCHAR2(10),
  rear_no     VARCHAR2(22),
  brch_no     VARCHAR2(22),
  id_card     VARCHAR2(30),
  max_xj      VARCHAR2(20) default 9999999,
  cus_no      VARCHAR2(10),
  phone_no    VARCHAR2(30),
  sys_brch_no VARCHAR2(22),
  xjye        NUMBER(12,2),
  qdsj        VARCHAR2(20),
  qtsj        VARCHAR2(20),
  dgrq        VARCHAR2(30),
  max_months  NUMBER,
  gy_power    VARCHAR2(30),
  ope_type    VARCHAR2(4),
  last_ztime  VARCHAR2(20),
  if_flag     VARCHAR2(4),
  ztimes      VARCHAR2(20),
  gyjb_b      VARCHAR2(4),
  bmrq_b      VARCHAR2(20),
  ymax_xj     VARCHAR2(20),
  brcn_no_b   VARCHAR2(8),
  box_flag    VARCHAR2(4),
  z_time      VARCHAR2(200)
)
tablespace RTRC_COMM
  pctfree 10
  initrans 1
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 10M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );
-- Add comments to the table 
comment on table GYXXB
  is '综合业务系统的柜员信息表';
-- Add comments to the columns 
comment on column GYXXB.gybh
  is '柜员编号';
comment on column GYXXB.gyxm
  is '柜员姓名';
comment on column GYXXB.bmrq
  is '密码变更日期';
comment on column GYXXB.gyzt
  is '柜员状态';
comment on column GYXXB.gyjb
  is '柜员级别 1:业务柜员  2:授权柜员';
comment on column GYXXB.rear_no
  is '柜员尾箱编号';
comment on column GYXXB.brch_no
  is '柜员所属网点编号';
comment on column GYXXB.id_card
  is '柜员身份证号';
comment on column GYXXB.max_xj
  is '现金最大值';
comment on column GYXXB.cus_no
  is '柜员客户编号';
comment on column GYXXB.phone_no
  is '柜员电话号码';
comment on column GYXXB.sys_brch_no
  is '系统机构号';
comment on column GYXXB.xjye
  is '现金余额';
comment on column GYXXB.gy_power
  is '柜员权限';
comment on column GYXXB.ope_type
  is '柜员类型';
comment on column GYXXB.last_ztime
  is '上次扎帐时间';
comment on column GYXXB.if_flag
  is '有效位0无效、1有效';
comment on column GYXXB.ztimes
  is '碰库次数';
comment on column GYXXB.gyjb_b
  is '原柜员级别';
comment on column GYXXB.bmrq_b
  is '更改日期';
comment on column GYXXB.ymax_xj
  is '原最大限额';
comment on column GYXXB.brcn_no_b
  is '更改前网点号';
comment on column GYXXB.box_flag
  is '是否有尾箱1-有，2-无';
comment on column GYXXB.z_time
  is '当日碰库明细';
-- Create/Recreate indexes 
create index INDEX_BRCH_NO on GYXXB (BRCH_NO)
  tablespace RTRC_COMM
  pctfree 10
  initrans 2
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 960K
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );
-- Create/Recreate primary, unique and foreign key constraints 
alter table GYXXB
  add constraint GYXXB_PK primary key (GYBH)
  using index 
  tablespace RTRC_COMM
  pctfree 10
  initrans 2
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 2M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );

)

  pctfree 10
  initrans 1
  maxtrans 255

  (
    initial 6M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );

-- 贷款信息表
-- Create table
create table LOAN_INFO
(
  acc_no        VARCHAR2(22),
  id_type       VARCHAR2(1),
  id_card       VARCHAR2(21),
  cus_name      VARCHAR2(62),
  str_date      VARCHAR2(10),
  exp_date      VARCHAR2(10),
  loan_term     VARCHAR2(2),
  item_no       VARCHAR2(8),
  loan_type     VARCHAR2(2),
  set_cycle     VARCHAR2(3),
  contract_no   VARCHAR2(30),
  loan_amount   VARCHAR2(15),
  int_rate      VARCHAR2(2),
  pay_mode      VARCHAR2(1),
  pay_acc_no    VARCHAR2(22),
  pay_name      VARCHAR2(62),
  collateral_no VARCHAR2(20),
  add_card_no   VARCHAR2(19),
  tran_time     VARCHAR2(19),
  flow_id       VARCHAR2(10),
  main_flow_id  VARCHAR2(20),
  deb_acc       VARCHAR2(22),
  occu_bank     VARCHAR2(5),
  loan_flag     VARCHAR2(2)
)
tablespace RTRC_STAT
  pctfree 10
  initrans 1
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 408M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  )
nologging;
-- Add comments to the columns 
comment on column LOAN_INFO.acc_no
  is '账号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.id_type
  is '证件类型';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.id_card
  is '证件号码';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.cus_name
  is '客户姓名';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.str_date
  is '起息日期';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.exp_date
  is '到期日期';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.loan_term
  is '贷款期限';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.item_no
  is '科目号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.loan_type
  is '贷款类型';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.set_cycle
  is '结息周期';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.contract_no
  is '核心录入号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.loan_amount
  is '贷款金额';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.int_rate
  is '利率调整';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.pay_mode
  is '贷款发放方式';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.pay_acc_no
  is '支付账号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.pay_name
  is '支付人姓名';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.collateral_no
  is '担保品编号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.add_card_no
  is '卡号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.tran_time
  is '开户时间';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.flow_id
  is '流水编号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.main_flow_id
  is '核心系统流水号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.deb_acc
  is '自动扣款账号';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.occu_bank
  is '交易网点';
comment on column LOAN_INFO.loan_flag
  is '扣款标记：0是：1否';
-- Create/Recreate indexes 
create index LOAN_INFO_INDEX_01 on LOAN_INFO (ACC_NO)
  tablespace RTRC_STAT
  pctfree 10
  initrans 2
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 112M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );

  tablespace RTRC_STAT
  pctfree 10

  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 80M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );

  tablespace RTRC_STAT
  pctfree 10
  initrans 2
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 51M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );

-- 账户信息表   为了提高索引的速度，依据账号的最后一位数将分户表分成了0-9 共10张表，其结构都是一样的
-- Create table
create table ZHXXB0
(
  d_acct      VARCHAR2(22) not null,
  d_accsi     VARCHAR2(6) not null,
  d_sbno      VARCHAR2(8),
  d_enddt     VARCHAR2(10),
  d_term1     VARCHAR2(2),
  d_idtp      VARCHAR2(1),
  d_idno      VARCHAR2(21),
  d_name      VARCHAR2(62),
  d_opndt     VARCHAR2(10),
  d_clipro    VARCHAR2(1),
  d_bale      NUMBER(12,2),
  d_drmod     VARCHAR2(1),
  d_accfg     VARCHAR2(1),
  d_optime    DATE,
  acc_type    VARCHAR2(1024),
  pro_code    VARCHAR2(4),
  update_time VARCHAR2(20),
  tran_flag   VARCHAR2(4)
)
tablespace RTRC_COMM
  pctfree 10
  initrans 1
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 2176M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );
-- Add comments to the columns 
comment on column ZHXXB0.acc_type
  is '历史记录';
comment on column ZHXXB0.pro_code
  is '产品代码';
comment on column ZHXXB0.update_time
  is '更新时间';
comment on column ZHXXB0.tran_flag
  is '是否发生交易标志';
-- Create/Recreate indexes 
create unique index ZHXXB0_UN__PK on ZHXXB0 (D_ACCT)
  tablespace RTRC_COMM
  pctfree 10
  initrans 2
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 776M
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );

-- 业务机构代码表
create table BUSINESS_BRCH
(
  opr_brch_no     VARCHAR2(16) not null,
  opr_brch_name   VARCHAR2(100),
  sys_brch_no     VARCHAR2(16),
  opr_brch_stat   VARCHAR2(1),
  opr_brch_type   VARCHAR2(1),
  logi_time       VARCHAR2(30),
  logo_time       VARCHAR2(30),
  opr_brch_tel    VARCHAR2(20),
  rule_grp        VARCHAR2(20),
  rear_max        VARCHAR2(20),
  defray_no       VARCHAR2(20),
  forex           VARCHAR2(1),
  custom_no       VARCHAR2(20),
  holiday_flag    VARCHAR2(1),
  singmax         VARCHAR2(20),
  summax          VARCHAR2(20),
  casebalance     VARCHAR2(20),
  cash_hour       VARCHAR2(1),
  canton_no       VARCHAR2(20),
  union_brch_no   VARCHAR2(100),
  brch_oper       VARCHAR2(100),
  brch_oper_photo VARCHAR2(20)
)
tablespace RTRC_COMM
  pctfree 10
  initrans 1
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 576K
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );
-- Add comments to the table 
comment on table BUSINESS_BRCH
  is '业务机构信息表';
-- Add comments to the columns 
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.opr_brch_no
  is '业务机构代码';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.opr_brch_name
  is '业务机构名称';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.sys_brch_no
  is '所属机构号';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.opr_brch_stat
  is '机构状态';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.opr_brch_type
  is '机构类型0储蓄所1分社2信用社3联社4市办';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.logi_time
  is '上次登入时间';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.logo_time
  is '上次登出时间';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.opr_brch_tel
  is '机构联系电话';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.rule_grp
  is '包涵规则组';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.rear_max
  is '尾箱限额';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.defray_no
  is '支付行号：支付业务时的唯一识别号';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.forex
  is '是否开通外汇业务：1-开通，0：未开通';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.custom_no
  is '客户号';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.holiday_flag
  is '是否休假1休假0不休假';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.singmax
  is '单笔贷款限额';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.summax
  is '累计贷款限额';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.casebalance
  is '现金余额';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.cash_hour
  is '现金在途时间：小时';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.canton_no
  is '行政代码';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.union_brch_no
  is '所属机构代码  一般为对应联社清算中心编码';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.brch_oper
  is '网点负责人';
comment on column BUSINESS_BRCH.brch_oper_photo
  is '负责人手机';
-- Create/Recreate primary, unique and foreign key constraints

  add constraint INDEX_BUSINESS_BRCH_PK primary key (OPR_BRCH_NO)
  using index 
  tablespace RTRC_COMM
  pctfree 10
  initrans 2
  maxtrans 255
  storage
  (
    initial 192K
    minextents 1
    maxextents unlimited
  );
